Grid Design Class

# Purpose of this class
To manage the entire grid

# Main attributes
- nodes (Node) : A list of nodes
- transmissions (str) : A list of all transmission lines
- graph : to represent the network connections

# Main methods
.add_node --> To add a generator or a consumer
.add_transmission --> To add a transmission line
.get_node --> To identify a node
.get_connected_nodes (Node) --> To get the list of connected nodes
.get_all_generators --> returns the list of generators
.get_all_consumers --> returns the list of consumers
